creator: Advenworks
descriptionHtml:
Zombies are invading your town! It is time to grab your gun, shoot them up and clean up the mess! No one prevents you from hanging out in town unpunished!
Begin your journey to stand among the zombies in this bold action survival game. Find your way in the apocalypse, upgrade your character & weapons, discover supplies to survive, and kill all zombies!
INTENSE ACTION
Kill never-ending waves of monsters and obstacles in this action-packed shooter. Each zombie have a special attack and behaviour. It is up to you to understand how they fight to defeat them.
AMAZING RPG GEAR UPGRADES & CHARACTER SKILLS
Unlock unique skills all designed to help you survive. Combien them to be the ultimate fighter. Unlock & upgrade hundreds of weapons, from handguns to powerful rocket launcher to rip through the undead.
EPIC LOOT FOR AN EPIC SURVIVAL
Find & loot pieces of armors, equipment & weapons during your adventure to improve your gear. Find & open chests to get special items to help you in your quest.
VAST WORLDS
Explore different worlds. Each of them has a different atmosphere and zombies. You have numerous places to defend!
CHALLENGING BOSS
Face formidable bosses with devastating special abilities. Win special prizes.
DAILY REWARDS
Get rewards everyday.
Any feedback, remark, question? Feel free to ask us anytime at: contact@advenworks.com
Terms of use - https://advenworks.com/terms-of-use/

title: Last Stand: Zombie Shooter

creator: Advenworks
descriptionHtml:
Zombies are invading your town! It is time to grab your gun, shoot them up and clean up the mess! No one prevents you from hanging out in town unpunished! That's a survival after all!

Help Jill to stand among the zombies in this bold action survival game. In Last Stand: Zombie Shooter, find your way in the apocalypse, upgrade your character & weapons, discover supplies to survive, and kill all zombies!

INTENSE ACTION
Kill never-ending waves of monsters and obstacles in this action-packed zombie shooter. Each zombie have a special attack and behaviour. It is up to you to understand how they fight to defeat them.

EASY GAMEPLAY
Slide your finger on the screen to move around. You fire automatically at zombies.

UPGRADE WEAPONS & CHARACTER
Upgrade your weapons to reach highest levels! Upgrade your character with talents to become stronger and faster! Become the ultimate survivor!

VARIOUS OBJECTIVES & MISSIONS
Complete special stages with many objectives: save a survivor, survive as long as possible, and many more!

GROW YOUR BASE
Build your base! Build shops, grow & harvest vegetables, own your animals, expand your base! Live fully the survival experience!

Last Stand: Zombie Shooter contains graphic violence (blood, zombies, monsters).

Any feedback, remark, question about Last Stand: Zombie Shooter? Feel free to ask us anytime at: contact@advenworks.com

Terms of use - https://advenworks.com/terms-of-use/

title: Last Stand: Zombie Shooter

creator: Advenworks
descriptionHtml:
Zombies are invading your town! It is time to grab your gun, shoot them up and clean up the mess! No one prevents you from hanging out in town unpunished! That's a survival after all!

Help Jill to stand among the zombies in this bold action survival game. In Last Stand: Zombie Shooter, find your way in the apocalypse, upgrade your character & weapons, discover supplies to survive, and kill all zombies!

INTENSE ACTION
Kill never-ending waves of monsters and obstacles in this action-packed zombie shooter. Each zombie have a special attack and behaviour. It is up to you to understand how they fight to defeat them.

EASY GAMEPLAY
Slide your finger on the screen to move around. You fire automatically at zombies.

UPGRADE WEAPONS & CHARACTER
Upgrade your weapons to reach highest levels! Upgrade your character with talents to become stronger and faster! Become the ultimate survivor!

VARIOUS OBJECTIVES & MISSIONS
Complete special stages with many objectives: save a survivor, survive as long as possible, and many more!

GROW YOUR BASE
Build your base! Build shops, grow & harvest vegetables, own your animals, expand your base! Live fully the survival experience!

Last Stand: Zombie Shooter contains graphic violence (blood, zombies, monsters).

Any feedback, remark, question about Last Stand: Zombie Shooter? Feel free to ask us anytime at: contact@advenworks.com

Terms of use - https://advenworks.com/terms-of-use/

title: Last Stand: Zombie Shooter

creator: Advenworks
descriptionHtml:
Immerse yourself in the ultimate survival game, Last Stand, where the Zombies and doom is just around the corner. In this arena of death, you are the hero standing against a horde of zombies in an epic game of survival. Your fortress? A world ravaged by fallout, where survival is the only rule.

Last Stand is packed with features designed to test your mettle. Engage in intense wargames with never-ending waves of zombies, each with their own unique attack patterns and behavior. Unlock all characters and choose your favorite, each with their own unique weapon and fighting style. Discover a host of weapons, from common to special, and upgrade them to their highest levels for maximum zombie-killing efficiency.

Your survival journey doesn't stop there. Complete various objectives and missions, like saving a survivor or surviving as long as possible. Build and grow your base, harvest vegetables, and expand your fortress to live the complete survival experience. Despite the intense action, the gameplay remains easy - simply slide your finger on the screen to move around, and you'll automatically fire at the zombies.

Prepare for the ultimate test of survival in a world where theft is a necessity and every resident is a potential specimen of the undead. Will you be the hitman that turns the tide, or will you fall to the zombie horde? Will you be the hero that stands at zero hour, or the victim of a vampire's bite? Only the raft of your courage can keep you afloat in this division of life and death.

Join the ranks of the brave and download Last Stand today. Stand among the ruins, face the doomsday, and be the last one standing. The dead walk, the doom is here, and the last stand is yours.

Any feedback, remark, question? Feel free to ask us anytime at: contact@advenworks.com
Terms of use - https://advenworks.com/terms-of-use/
